  08 Feb 2009; Arun Raghavan <ford_prefect@gentoo.org>
  glipper-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Use split gnome-python* dependencies. Thanks to Nirbheek Chauhan
  <nirbheek.chauhan@gmail.com>. Bug #257818

  18 Jun 2008; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> -glipper-1.0.ebuild,
  -glipper-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Cleanup.

  29 May 2008; Ali Polatel <hawking@gentoo.org> glipper-1.0.ebuild,
  glipper-1.0-r1.ebuild, glipper-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  python_mod_optimize is ROOT aware. Multilib love.

*glipper-1.0-r2 (23 Mar 2008)

  23 Mar 2008; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org>
  +files/glipper-1.0-transparent.patch, +glipper-1.0-r2.ebuild:
  Revision bump, include a patch to make the applet icon transparent, bug
  #212265.

*glipper-1.0-r1 (03 Jan 2008)

  03 Jan 2008; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org>
  +files/glipper-1.0-binary-data.patch, +glipper-1.0-r1.ebuild:
  Pull in a patch from upstream that should fix binary data clipboard items.
  This should fix bug #177461.

  22 Sep 2007; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> -glipper-0.95.1.ebuild,
  -glipper-0.95.1-r1.ebuild:
  Cleanup.

  11 Sep 2007; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> glipper-1.0.ebuild:
  Add missing dependencies, move dependencies to both DEPEND and RDEPEND, bug
  #176421.

  10 Sep 2007; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> glipper-1.0.ebuild:
  Install gconf schema files.

*glipper-1.0 (09 Sep 2007)

  09 Sep 2007; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> +glipper-1.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

*glipper-0.95.1-r1 (05 Mar 2007)

  05 Mar 2007; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> +glipper-0.95.1-r1.ebuild:
  Add support for the gnome USE flag, thanks to Oliver Schinagl and Jakub Moc
  in bug #158590.

  09 Jan 2007; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> glipper-0.95.1.ebuild:
  Add proper autotoold dependency for bug #158535.

  07 Dec 2006; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> glipper-0.95.1.ebuild:
  Add missing gnome-doc-utils dependency, bug #157461.

